title: Wildcards Siege is live! #R6S

author: Ubisoft
description:
From December 15th to January 5th, join the exclusive Wildcards Siege event celebrating a decade of Siege. 

Battle it out where it all began on House map packed with easter eggs and callbacks to Siege’s earliest days. Jump into an explosive Bomb game mode where iconic modifiers like Original Recruits and ACOG-only await and bring back the feel of classic matches.

About Rainbow Six Siege X:
Rainbow Six Siege X is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege X is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

#Ubisoft #R6SiegeX
